    "description": "在《沙尘与霓虹》中，死亡只是开始，这是一款融入roguelite元素的双摇杆动作射击游戏，以恶棍横行的后末日西部荒野为故事背景。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1296450/extras/814b05405d4cd7a6521c21639de1d0ff.poster.avif?t=1699463400\" width=600 height=254 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1296450/extras/814b05405d4cd7a6521c21639de1d0ff.webm?t=1699463400\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1296450/extras/814b05405d4cd7a6521c21639de1d0ff.mp4?t=1699463400\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>玩家在游戏中扮演一名神秘枪侠，踏上一段史诗般的征程，历练精准枪法，激烈枪战一触即发。玩家需要应对来势汹汹的机器人军队，还有异常激烈的boss战斗。如果起初你没有成功，不要轻言放弃，你可以使用数十种待解锁的技能、数千种各具特色的武器以及可以扭转战局的强化道具继续尝试，让你的英雄势不可挡。<br><br>警告：《沙尘与霓虹》并不是一款能够轻松通关的游戏。如果你想挑战一下自己的技能，那你可找对游戏了。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >开枪扫射……全面开火</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1296450/extras/f9b455f7c6b552211a7883e5e3f3d0cf.poster.avif?t=1699463400\" width=600 height=254 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1296450/extras/f9b455f7c6b552211a7883e5e3f3d0cf.webm?t=1699463400\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1296450/extras/f9b455f7c6b552211a7883e5e3f3d0cf.mp4?t=1699463400\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>这是一款极富挑战性且融入了roguelite元素的双摇杆射击游戏，采用自装弹机制——将每一颗子弹在激烈的枪战中压入弹膛。采用一流控制设计，为玩家带来快速精准的射击游戏体验。游戏采用动态强化道具系统，能让玩家一口气操作干掉机械敌人。装弹和制定下一步行动策略的同时，进行闪躲、滑行、并无缝连接寻找掩护。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >收集和升级你的武器库</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1296450/extras/cc825e5ff14bfa614bc9c40b6680c73e.poster.avif?t=1699463400\" width=600 height=254 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1296450/extras/cc825e5ff14bfa614bc9c40b6680c73e.webm?t=1699463400\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1296450/extras/cc825e5ff14bfa614bc9c40b6680c73e.mp4?t=1699463400\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>游戏中有将近2000支各具特色的左轮手枪、霰弹枪和步枪等待玩家解锁和选用。1600种各不相同的补给品可以让你暂时扭转战局或强化你的战斗力，游戏中还有数百个装满钱、武器和升级道具的宝箱等着你去打开。玩家可以用24种独特的技能升级你的枪手，打造个性十足的游戏玩法。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >死亡只是开始</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1296450/extras/2676b7bc8e68295377b7ede9922b4ef8.poster.avif?t=1699463400\" width=600 height=254 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1296450/extras/2676b7bc8e68295377b7ede9922b4ef8.webm?t=1699463400\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1296450/extras/2676b7bc8e68295377b7ede9922b4ef8.mp4?t=1699463400\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>游戏中战役的时长超过15小时，专为敢于接受挑战的你而准备！完美主义玩家会发现有更多的冒险时间在等着他们。探索一个由四个不同区域组成的宏大的多样化世界，与一群各具优势与弱点的机器人敌人展开战斗。在史诗般的boss战中挑战各式各样的邪恶反派，获得奖励。",
